<title>USA: Sylvan Learning completes acquisition.</title>
<headline>Sylvan Learning completes acquisition.</headline>
<dateline>BALTIMORE 1997-06-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>Sylvan Learning Systems Inc said Tuesday it completed the acquisition of I-R, Inc and Independent Child Study Teams Inc.</p>
<p>The company issued 1.4 million shares of Sylvan Common Stock which, based on the June 9, 1997 closing price of Sylvan's stock, would value the transaction at approximately $50.2 million. The transaction will be accounted for as a pooling of interest and the Company expects it to be accretive to 1997 earnings.</p>
</text>
